# Step 3

Run the app:

```bash
flutter run
```

or build a new APK:

```bash
flutter build apk
```

---

# Expected Result

The app should now follow this flow:

```text
Splash Screen
      ↓
Login Screen
      ↓
(Home button)
      ↓
Home Screen
```

The Login button doesn't validate credentials yet—it simply takes the user to the Home Screen. We'll connect it to the backend in the coming days.

